{"tid":664464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普說大了？白宮解畫：美遵從法規處理中興","createTime":"2018-05-14T05:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T16:56:36.000Z","uid":4783,"like":82,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"fde95bc72661662fb718d2bb0a82caaf31f3ca6c","tid":664464,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:58:15.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗昨夜在推特發聲，暗示或放生中興通訊，與此前打出「合規牌」企硬的態度迥異，在美國輿論場引起反彈。白宮隨即解畫，重申美方會遵循適用法律法規，美國商務部會運用獨立判斷，決定如何處置中興。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普當地時間13日在Twitter上發文稱，習近平和他正在共同工作，為中興通訊提供一條快速恢復業務的途徑，否則中國會流失太多工作崗位，他已指示商務部完成這項工作。<br />\n<br />\n白宮發言人 特朗普只是強調「互惠」<br />\n<br />\n鑒於特朗普所發推文意思不清晰，白宮特此發出了一則聲明，表示中興通訊的問題將由商務部獨立裁決。<br />\n<br />\n白宮發言人Lindsay Walters證實，美國官員正在就中興問題與中方接觸。她表示，特朗普的推文強調了中美之間在涉及經濟、貿易和投資等問題方面，「自由、公平、平衡和互惠的關係是至關重要的」。<br />\n<br />\n但她強調，特朗普認為，商務部長羅斯「將行使其獨立判斷，遵照有關法律法規，以事實為基礎，解決涉及中興通訊的監管行動」。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部、中興和中國駐華大使館暫未對特朗普的表述置評。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，白宮解畫的同時，特朗普暗示「放生」中興，在美國政界引起反彈。有政界人物擔心特朗普為得到與中方的商貿利益，犧牲美國的安全。<br />\n<br />\n美政界人士：美國安全比中國就業重要<br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院情報委員會（House Intelligence Committee）級別最高的民主黨人士、加州議員Adam Schiff認同這些擔憂，他在Twitter上回應特朗普的言論時表示，美國情報機構已警告，中興通訊的技術和手機構成重大網絡安全威脅。<br />\n<br />\n他責備特朗普稱，相比中國的就業崗位，特朗普應該更加在意美國國家安全。<br />\n<br />\n參議院少數黨領袖、紐約州民主黨議員舒默（Chuck Schumer）在Twitter上回應特朗普時表示，「何不先幫助一些美國公司」？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2072384/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%AA%AA%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%9F%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E8%A7%A3%E7%95%AB%EF%BC%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%87%E9%81%B5%E5%BE%9E%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%8F%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%88?mtc=30008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2072384%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BA%2586%25EF%25BC%259F%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25AE%25AE%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E7%2595%25AB%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%2581%25B5%25E5%25BE%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%258F%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2588%2588%3Fmtc%3D30008&d=fq0aq0RQIHg2u0X0ok2fbjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=e3f4e2a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2072384/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%AA%AA%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%9F%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E8%A7%A3%E7%95%AB%EF%BC%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%87%E9%81%B5%E5%BE%9E%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%8F%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%88?mtc=30008</a>"},{"pid":"edac16c052f759099e8f78b4d79b5ce9b8add3da","tid":664464,"uid":4783,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:59:32.000Z","msg":"俾埋英文SOURCE你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nWhite House spokeswoman Lindsay Walters confirmed that U.S. officials were in contact with Beijing about ZTE. She said Trump&rsquo;s tweet underscored the importance of &ldquo;free, fair, balanced and mutually beneficial&rdquo; relations between the United States and China on issues involving the economy, trade and investment.<br />\n<br />\nTrump expects Commerce Secretary Wilbur Ross &ldquo;to exercise his independent judgment, consistent with applicable laws and regulations, to resolve the regulatory action involving ZTE based on its facts,&rdquo; Walters said.<br />\n<br />\nTrump&rsquo;s announcement drew sharp criticism from a Democratic lawmaker, who said the move was jeopardizing U.S. national security.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Our intelligence agencies have warned that ZTE technology and phones pose a major cyber security threat,&rdquo; Representative Adam Schiff said on Twitter. &ldquo;You should care more about our national security than Chinese jobs.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-china-zte/in-concession-trump-will-help-chinas-zte-get-back-into-business-idUSKCN1IE0QI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-china-zte%2Fin-concession-trump-will-help-chinas-zte-get-back-into-business-idUSKCN1IE0QI&d=fq0aq0RQIHg2u0X0ok2fbjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b5f8e8eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-china-zte%2Fin-concession-trump-will-help-chinas-zte-get-back-into-business-idUSKCN1IE0QI&h=df63b154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-china-zte/in-concession-trump-will-help-chinas-zte-get-back-into-business-idUSKCN1IE0QI</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨關心制裁仲多過共和黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60515f783a4f8df977681cd79d775869b5e0bc67","tid":664464,"uid":2644,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:00:21.000Z","msg":"來回地獄又折返人間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f92f0f29459d2e29f6dfd7008752ab090fa0dd","tid":664464,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed3521b306e0b9c341b77913c674fcfca6de530","tid":664464,"uid":25468,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:04:18.000Z","msg":"5 毛炒車 ?"},{"pid":"d02d1b4c033081b3404fd4c9ffd09580797dd45e","tid":664464,"uid":38982,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:04:30.000Z","msg":"美國識玩, 學埋中共招亂搬龍門, 扯貓尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89e522ebf815ec81cd29439720160dd10f0b263","tid":664464,"uid":74935,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:05:30.000Z","msg":"[quote]<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/14/134009_5b1d4384a30bdaa65213d6c49dd85868.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2F134009_5b1d4384a30bdaa65213d6c49dd85868.png&h=990ebbb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60b2e3b82513bb3fea6476df7170040fe56a13dc","tid":664464,"uid":45353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:06:57.000Z","msg":"其實政棍講野真係唔好睇表面推斷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />